citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 1:20pm -
2:00pm on 03-May-18.
We knocked on house door, honked the vehicle horn, and left a message on licensee's phone.
Additional Inspectors
Heine William, Animal Care Inspector
